{"tid":1803932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【200萬和理非】完全發揮唔到作用，除非...","createTime":"2019-12-30T14:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:58:37.000Z","uid":135332,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe9fccc3b37974ff357b02701a3e611624b6feb","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[代友Post]</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n除非呢200萬一齊出現...</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[原Post - <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1799750/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1799750/page/1</a>]</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下討論是 for <span style=\"color: red;\">永遠做合法野的和理非</span>，尤其是睇完屌和理非不合作的POST，總覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">200萬和理非的效用完全發揮唔到</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">利申：本人感激每位手足，尤其是前線，以下內容不是抹殺前線功勞，只是想探討和理非如何多踏一步。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過實戰，和你SHOP成效絕對係有，可以每星期六日運作，對增強良心經濟圏非常有用，起碼抵制了無良奸商，<span style=\"color: red;\">觸動政府神經 [=錢]</span>；另外借力打力等等等等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">利申：作為一個徹頭徹尾的和理非，我其實好建議這類和平行動，因為我覺得成個計劃可100%完全合法進行，不需送頭。</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">[e.g. 以成就稍差的時代為例，如果Shopping Queue夠長，可以逐間逐間名店入去，入到嗌口號又好，唱歌報佳音又好，拎旗又好，著到光鮮靚靚又好，不停插嘴中斷招呼緊大陸客的職員又好，左望右望睇下買咩野又好；就算唔入名店，在門口10個人喪跑/轉圏/唱歌/呼叫已經好OK] </span>但當然，每每見到有人送頭，總覺不甘，<span style=\"color: red;\">作為和理非好想再行一步</span>。<br />\n<br />\n但正正因為和理非係比較和理，除非本身已經約左10+個朋友 Shopping，否則，就我所見，和理非都係企係度多，和應下口號，嗌口號成粒鐘，最後興味索然走人算。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係和理非，試過去到現場聚左人但其實無實質行動，請keep reading。</span><br />\n<br />\n為解決呢個問題，其實<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非需要Join埋一齊出現，一齊完成任務</span>，先唔會浪費左你抽空出現的時間。就<span style=\"color: red;\">好似玩大學Ocamp咁</span>，1個人係條街扮狗叫當然唔敢，但10+個Ocamp人成隊扮狗叫，通常10個都敢，而通常呢10個仲要係唔識對方 [迎新營呀嘛]。人多，就唔會覺得入名店叫口號係Mission Impossible，即使係和理非。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但，無端端三唔識七，點會一齊出現呢?</span> <br />\n偉大的 Telegram 幫到你。但需要有<span style=\"color: red;\">預設的 Ground Rules</span> 和破壞 Rules 的 Punishment。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">首先，要有個人(最好係會落街參與和你SHOP的和理非，不是冷氣軍師) 開1個TG Group，目標是~ 20人，人滿就不再recruit，因為人多怕訊息太亂。點解20個人? 差不多Ocamp一隊人數，同埋不是次次任務都會100% attendance。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Ground Rules：</span><br />\nGroup入面<br />\n(1) 唔可以講犯法野<br />\n(2) 唔可以鼓勵犯法野<br />\n(3) 唔可以問/講 Personal details<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[大家都知邊d可講，我在龍門冰室都同對面阿嬏暢所欲言啦，但唔會無端端自爆名字/電話]</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Punishment：</span><br />\n其實好簡單，邊個組員犯規，踢佢出Group；或者，Admin係鬼，想chok大家Personal野/講犯法野，大家自己退Group/另開Group。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知，<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非的好處是：做野永遠合法，beyond reproach，所以form group都唔需太避忌，有鬼超易捉[一講犯法野即踢走]。</span>而入過大Group就知：成日無端端捉鬼，跟住重要任務其間就被捉鬼msg洗版哂，如果一個和理非入左大Group，真係唔知講咩好，明明和你Shop本來可以(扮)和平進行。當然，有勇武幫手，事情發展會快d，但係咁代表要送頭，和理非如果連線到，可能唔需要再送頭，或者送頭大大減低可能。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">咁form左個TG group，咁又點呢？</span><br />\n咁就可以<span style=\"color: red;\">約實時間一齊10+人玩Ocamp，完成合法任務</span> [可抄上述時代商場e.g./參照連登Post下討論]。約實咩時間等[最好跟文宣集合時間]，咩位置等[e.g. 時代2/F]。差不多齊人 [如果想更多人，當然亦可以問下隔離team &ldquo;shopping tgt ma?&rdquo;]，就可以自由發揮，嗌口號/lead唱歌/大嗌&ldquo;Shopping shopping&rdquo;入名店&hellip;等等等合法任務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">!!! 重要重要重要 !!!</span> <span style=\"color: red;\"> 任務期間，如果發現有組員想做犯法野，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔使勸/阻/幫/cover/捉鬼</span></span>，大家自動波走開，繼續real or fake shopping，總之和理非係隨時可real隨時可fake，大家憑自己原則做野/走開。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">咁邊個人 form group？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Any 和理非</span>，尤其是發現成日去到但無咩發揮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建議想玩Ocamp朋友，下面可留言 TG group link + Ground Rules；至於無連登Acc的和理非[相信佔大多數]，請按自己shopping喜好入Group，20人左右好了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Template：<br />\n(1)<br />\n描述：星期六 &ndash; 時代 <br />\n要求：永遠合法<br />\n(2)<br />\n描述：星期六日 &ndash; 沙田 <br />\n要求：永遠合法 + 街坊look preferred<br />\n(3)<br />\n描述：星期日5點後 &ndash; 大埔<br />\n要求：永遠合法 + 不介意留到深夜<br />\n(4)<br />\n描述：平日放工後 &ndash; 沙田<br />\n要求：永遠合法 <br />\n(5)<br />\n描述：平日放工後 &ndash; 時代<br />\n要求：永遠合法 + 不介意係中庭放文宣在地下<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n等等等等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重有一點：互相監察</span></span>，唔係叫你捉鬼，而係一見面，大家有共識咁拉下件衫/攝衫+唔好帶earphone&hellip; 雖然唔預做犯法野，但都用2秒check下，買個安心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認為有用，請<span style=\"color: red;\">推上熱門</span>；希望除左有五毛拉，都有真手足推，<span style=\"color: red;\">最好下方有Group Link出現 [<span style=\"color: green;\">原Post已經有啦</span>]，俾大量無連登戶口人加入Group</span>。Group Link 希望在 TG 各平台都見到。<br />\n<br />\n200萬人，假設20人一組，都有10萬組啦，時代一層一組20人圍住店舖練跑/名店門前拎camera不停flashlight影相趕客，點都得啦!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">記住：以上建議，永遠合法者最為適用。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">多你一個好多，本身已經做慣admin/有太空卡的麻煩整多d TG group比人join</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好成日屌和理非唔合作，大家要揾岩合作模式，遷就唔同人。</span>"},{"pid":"b57200d8a612ee0d62c2d42f7ef89ffa8882b323","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"偉大的 Telegram <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7faeb8ed4d5c9814f37fd791038aef7f52cd42f","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"和理非真係最持久戰的一群"},{"pid":"e9c7f4f07c5133e2217d22be23b60f351c990645","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5459d58fa16f1f314ef5cb4a90d8ea7c673bcff","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"需要有預設的 Ground Rules &lt;= 呢個重要，'永遠合法' 是其一。"},{"pid":"bc73740ccec6d11127a953f7f722bbd356eafc88","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最關鍵 ---&gt;</span> 做任務其間，如果發現有組員想做犯法野，唔使勸/阻/幫/cover/捉鬼，大家自動波走開，繼續real or fake shopping，總之和理非係隨時可real隨時可fake，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家憑自己原則做野/走開</span>。"},{"pid":"2f652187b38751be8d45a03ea72bfe81074f69f0","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"Ocamp d 任務其實都好擾民，好岩用。"},{"pid":"6d0d5fca1f39255c28a9860223366b852822442c","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"而家已經係長期抗爭mode，方法的確值得做。"},{"pid":"d8dd4168ab9b4091021a1705fe36afce0d1a3eec","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"有用post一定要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f52b1566f4a22208dada4101491aa7171dda5e","tid":1803932,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"實際有用，長期抗爭，總不能次次送頭。"},{"pid":"f927859ee73b8bce8771f5e1a66c41cd3b438fd4","tid":1803932,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s